OL,3,CPerranporth man recalls being swept up
OL,4,Cby the Boxing Day tsunami 20 years ago
OL,6,FOn December 26 2004, a 9.1 magnitude
OL,7,Fearthquake under the sea triggered one
OL,8,Fof the deadliest disasters in modern
OL,9,Fhistory.
OL,11,FThe Boxing Day Tsunami slammed in to
OL,12,F14 countries around the Indian Ocean,
OL,13,Fincluding Sri Lanka, where Daniel
OL,14,FPoole from Perranporth was on a surf
OL,15,Ftrip.
