OL,3,CPerranporth man recalls being swept up
OL,4,Cby the Boxing Day tsunami 20 years ago
OL,6,FDaniel recalled the moment the tsunami
OL,7,Fstruck - "Boxing Day morning we were
OL,8,Fwoken to the sounds of shouting,
OL,9,Fprimal screams, I jumped up, and
OL,10,Fpulled the cloth back and looked out
OL,11,Fand we could see this big wall of
OL,12,Fwhite water coming in across the sea,
OL,13,Fit was bigger than any of the waves
OL,14,Fthat we'd been surfing."
