OL,3,CPerranporth man recalls being swept up
OL,4,Cby the Boxing Day tsunami 20 years ago
OL,6,FHe added "It marched over where we
OL,7,Fwere staying, we were kind of swept
OL,8,Foff our feet by the water, and then
OL,9,Fthe roof dropped down onto us, and
OL,10,Fthat's the last like the last time I
OL,11,Fremember seeing the room and being
OL,12,Fabove water for a couple of seconds
OL,13,Fwhen we get washed through the back
OL,14,Fwall of the building and then through
OL,15,Fthe compound wall, all of this were
OL,16,Funder water and then across a service
OL,17,Fditch and then a road and then we were
OL,18,Fswept up into the jungle."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
