OL,3,CPerranporth man recalls being swept up
OL,4,Cby the Boxing Day tsunami 20 years ago
OL,6,F"I grabbed my partner and I managed to
OL,7,Fget her up onto this pile of debris
OL,8,Fwhere she could be out of the water, I
OL,9,Fmanaged to climb up and her, and we
OL,10,Fjust kind of looked around and the sea
OL,11,Fwas just below us, it was all of a
OL,12,Fsudden in a whole new position, it was
OL,13,Fjust the strangest thing".
