OL,3,CPerranporth man recalls being swept up
OL,4,Cby the Boxing Day tsunami 20 years ago
OL,6,FMark said he was shocked by the
OL,7,Fdevastation he witnessed "seeing how
OL,8,Fpeople live or how they're coping,
OL,9,Fhaving lost everything, but also the
OL,10,Fresilience in those individuals and
OL,11,Fhow they're just ready to to pick up
OL,12,Fand move on and what we were able to
OL,13,Fprovide, albeit very little at the
OL,14,Ftime, gave at least 300 families
OL,15,Fshelter".
OL,17,FTsunami: The Wave That Shook the World
OL,18,Fairs on 27 December on ITV1 and ITVX.
